responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "27AFF77D4A68BB0D0E710AA4E72EDF49", "\"Windswept moor, a lake now foul and unclean, the war is gone and empires are unseen. Within the aftermath and madness the alpha is laid to rest. A tall strong oak, on edges of green where battles did roam. A howling hero is buried beneath. Yet arcane essence in air is played, upon and within a twin flute hanging from tree. It is in this howl of oak that sometimes the alpha doth return, to attack and defend,\" ")
name: LADD_0002_THO_Book_TheHowlingOak_7
